  <brief_title>A Post-Market Clinical Trial for Access and Visualization of the Oropharynx, Hypopharynx and Larynx During Transoral Procedures</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter OUS Post-Market Clinical Follow-Up of the Medrobotics Flex® Robotic System Used for Accessing and Visualizing the Oropharynx, Hypopharynx, and Larynx During Transoral Procedures</official_title>
